    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>1 to 2 lbs milkfish, cleaned and sliced</li><li>1 bunch mustard leaves</li><li>3 medium tomatoes, quartered</li><li>1 pack (1.4 ounces) tamarind soup mix</li><li>2½ tablespoons fish sauce</li><li>2 pieces long green chilies (siling pansigang)</li><li>½ cup white or yellow miso (soybean paste)</li><li>1 medium yellow onion, sliced</li><li>2 tablespoons cooking oil</li><li>6 cups water</li></ul>",
