    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>2 cups (1 can) coconut milk</li><li>2 cups (1 can) coconut cream</li><li>12 ounces canned tuna (in water)</li><li>5 to 8 pieces dried red chili pepper</li><li>3 cups dried chopped kale leaves</li><li>¼ cup sliced ginger</li><li>1 teaspoon minced garlic</li><li>¼ cup spicy shrimp paste (bagoong)</li></ul>",
