    "ingredients" : "<ul><li>1 large milkfish, deboned</li><li>½ cup chopped parsley</li><li>1 head garlic, crushed</li><li>3 tablespoons olive oil</li><li>1 teaspoon coarse sea salt</li><li>¼ teaspoon ground black pepper</li></ul>",
